It is a web site on which people can seek for useful tip to improve effectiveness.

The first step is going to share my tip to attract eyes.

Functionalities:

 1. what is a tip?
   It is a sequence of words no more than 88
   it includes the issue resolved,benefit,solution.
 
 2. post a tip,modify a tip,delete a tip
 
 
 3.tip can have tags
 
 4.cut off the tip which is too long in the list page
